column5: Got an email this morning from Bass Pro with a huge deal on Humminbird Fishfinder 768 on sale for $199!!! If you're looking don't wait as supplies are limited.

"originally $499.99" is somewhat misleading. The "regular" price is listed as $299.99.  http://www.basspro.c..._BOEbq5B8cIh6NW  Still a deal I suppose but not quite the "incredible one time offer".  .  Just my 199 cents (regularly 499 cents) worth. Slayer
They weren't when I posted this. I said they would go fast.
